This is the PHP binding to the Rackspace Cloud Monitoring API

http://www.rackspace.com/cloud/cloud_hosting_products/monitoring

at the moment it has had one sitting of programming generally Friday afternoons is do what you want time...
litrally... games, code... whatever... so non important bug fixes would get done on fridays or before if i get board for
a few minutes.

This PHP Libary is supported by Original Webware Limited
Please report any issue or idea to the bug tracker here:

https://github.com/snider/php-cloudMonitoring/issues

We also make the PHP Cloud DNS api and respond quick to peoples ideas, code patches etc so please get in touch with ideas... it helps!

